/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  dMSans: "DM Sans",
  poppins: "Poppins",
  inter: "Inter",
  roboto: "Roboto",
  josefinSans: "Josefin Sans",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_3xs: 10,
  size_lg: 18,
  size_mini: 15,
  size_8xl: 27,
  size_base: 16,
  size_3xl: 22,
  size_xs: 12,
  size_sm: 14,
  size_smi: 13,
  size_7xl: 26,
  size_xl: 20,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  colorWhitesmoke_100: "#f9f9f9",
  colorWhitesmoke_300: "#f6f6f6",
  colorGray_100: "#fefefe",
  colorGray_200: "#888",
  gray_100: "#797979",
  colorSeagreen: "#4b8364",
  colorWhite: "#fff",
  colorDarkslategray: "#333",
  khaki: "rgba(218, 214, 131, 0.63)",
  colorBlack: "#000",
  colorRoyalblue_100: "#5676dc",
  darkturquoise: "#11bad0",
  colorDimgray_100: "#6c6c6c",
  colorDimgray_200: "#666",
  colorDimgray_300: "#555",
  colorMediumvioletred: "#e33589",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_33xl: 52,
  p_lg: 18,
  p_30xl: 49,
  p_7xl: 26,
  p_4xl: 23,
  p_8xl: 27,
  p_11xs: 2,
  p_8xs: 5,
  p_5xs: 8,
  p_6xs: 7,
  p_3xs: 10,
  p_2xs: 11,
  p_2xl: 21,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_7xs: 6,
  br_11xs: 2,
  br_3xs: 10,
  br_9xs: 4,
  br_61xl: 80,
  br_8xs: 5,
  br_6xs: 7,
};
